      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering with this E46 M3. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a mechanical M-variable limited-slip differential. This example is mechanically robust, with the critical rod bearing service and rear subframe reinforcement already completed. The suspension geometry remains precise, benefiting from refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers. While the exterior shows the honest character of a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains tight, providing the tactile feedback and linear torque curve that defined an era of BMW M performance.",
